/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈內容包括：</span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a759078b3ebe01be9e6a4b212e2503c3fd2d9b52","tid":1537833,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"葵公有冇得諗 個位容唔容易走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd713d0e64d020c4fa4cc67a2a128d976a842ef8","tid":1537833,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67028777f4f26d51db171a4d29e967c26d3c7ca1","tid":1537833,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533ab63b98202851c369f88380fbdff46e01f30a","tid":1537833,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"唔好諗 守<br />\n得攻同散"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"要癱瘓半日 